One thing you should remember when you are trying new activities is safety first

00:00:27.730 --> 00:00:32.309
You'll notice that I forgot my helmet and my knee pads and my elbow pads.

00:00:32.309 --> 00:00:35.819
I really should have those, but I forgot them.

