00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:11.280
I'm finding that with a

00:01:11.619 --> 00:01:15.779
prosthetic on the left, it's a little bit difficult to swing your leg

00:01:16.990 --> 00:01:18.790
from your bike

00:01:18.790 --> 00:01:25.019
over,  because you have to rotate your foot, and you put ends up kind of out of whack. So, for example if I start here

00:01:27.549 --> 00:01:32.999
Swing over. Kinda awkward. Swinging back is even more awkward.

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:39.100
So I thought about

00:01:39.979 --> 00:01:41.869
going from the other side.

